Package org.openadaptor.auxil.expression.function

Class Summary
AbstractFunction Abstract base class for function implementations.
AdaptorStartFn Function to provide access to the Adaptor start timestamp as a Date.
DateFn Function to convert a long value into a Date().
DateParseFn Function to parse Dates supplied as Stringvalues.
EndsWithFn Evaluate String.endsWith()
FloorFn Function to implement Math.floor().
FormatFn Formatting functions.
IsNullFn Replaces NULL with the specified replacement value in much the same fashion as the isNull() function in T-SQL.
LengthFn Function to implement String.length().
LowerFn Implementation of String.toLowerCase()
MatchesFn Function to implement String.matches().
NowFn Generate a java.util.Date object representing the current date/time.
RoundFn Function to implement Math.round().
StartsWithFn Evaluate String.startsWith()
SubstringFn implements a String.substring() function.
SystemPropertyFn Function to provide access to System Properties.
TrimFn Implementation of String.trim()
UpperFn Implementation of String.toUpperCase()
